Terms were made with nations on the spot, the frontier all along was carefully laid out and strengthened by colonies and military posts³3 the ‘limes' beyond the Rhine, commenced by previous emperors and carried on by Domitian, was further extended and now included definitely within the empire the ‘agri decumates‚' and gave the Romanized settlers a saie looting on that once debatable land⁴.
